sequenceDiagram
  participant A as 客户端 A (持有锁)
  participant B as 客户端 B (等待锁)
  participant R as Redis (锁状态)
  participant E as etcd (事件通知)

  B->>R: SET lock uuidB NX PX 30000
  R-->>B: nil (加锁失败)
  B->>E: Watch /notify/lock (阻塞等待事件)
  A->>R: EVAL 释放锁 (lua: GET==uuidA 则 DEL)
  A->>E: Put /notify/lock (触发释放事件)
  E-->>B: Watch 回调: /notify/lock 有 PUT 事件
  B->>R: SET lock uuidB NX PX 30000
  R-->>B: OK (加锁成功)
